HEADWORD: Alfet
<hw>Al"fet</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL. <ets>alfetum</ets>, fr. AS.
<ets>⟦amac⟧lf⟦ae⟧t</ets> a pot to boil in; <ets>⟦amac⟧l</ets> burning +
<ets>f⟦ae⟧t</ets> vat.]</ety> <def>A caldron of boiling water into which
